   DiscussionThese data provide the first large-scale normative data for the EPSI in young adults, as well as additional evidence supporting the psychometric properties and construct validity of the EPSI. (c) 2013 Wiley Periodicals, Inc. (Int J Eat Disord 2014; 47:85-91)
